### Variables
@host = http://localhost:8080

### ─── LOGIN ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login com ADMIN (copiar o token e colar em @JWT_TOKEN abaixo)
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "AdminSenha@123"
}

###

### Login com USER
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao3@example.com",
  "password": "Senha@123"
}

###

### usar para ADMIN:
#@JWT_TOKEN =

### usar para USER:
@JWT_TOKEN = SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### INSTRUÇÕES:
### 1. Execute "Login com ADMIN" acima
### 2. Copie o token JWT do response
### 3. Cole o token em: @JWT_TOKEN = SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
### 4. Execute os demais requests

### ─── PROJECTS – CRUD ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Criar project
POST {{host}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Residencial Vista Verde",
  "address": "Rua das Palmeiras, 100 – Curitiba, PR",
  "projectType": "RESIDENTIAL",
  "category": "BUILDING",
  "landArea": 800.00,
  "builtArea": 600.00,
  "status": "PLANNING",
  "plannedStartDate": "2024-03-01",
  "plannedEndDate": "2025-06-30"
}

###

### Listar todos os projects
GET {{host}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

###

### Buscar project por ID
GET {{host}}/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

###

### Atualizar project (PATCH /projects/{id})
PATCH {{host}}/projects/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Residencial Vista Verde – Fase 2",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "plannedEndDate": "2025-09-30"
}

###

### Excluir project (DELETE /projects/{id})
DELETE {{host}}/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

### ─── ACOMPANHAMENTO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Acompanhamento de project por ID (mock com dados aleatórios por ID)
GET {{host}}/projects/1/acompanhamento
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

###

### Acompanhamento – project 2
GET {{host}}/projects/2/acompanhamento
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

###

### Acompanhamento – project 3
GET {{host}}/projects/3/acompanhamento
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}
